fall television schedule. On the ad agency side, dozens of
executives are responsible for previewing the networks' fall
schedules in May and June and deciding which programs will be hits.
By Greg Farrell.
</P>
<P>
   BANANA-ECONSCENE (Undated) _ Few Americans care whether Europe
buys bananas from Ecuador, Guatemala or Honduras. So many wondered
whether the Clinton administration recklessly started a trade war
when it announced this week a list of European luxury products that
it vowed to tax into extinction if the European Union did not open
its borders to bananas from Latin America. By Michael M. Weinstein.
