 &HT;    EMBARGOED UNTIL DECEMBER 27
 &HT;    The year in style
 &HT;    By A. Scott Walton
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   It's abundantly clear from the looks showcased in our second
annual InStyle calendar that there's much to look forward to
wearing in the coming year.
</P>
<P>
   When we asked retailers to send us the best styles they had for
each month of the year, they responded by selecting clothes that
emphasize luxurious fabrication, comfort tailoring and cheerful
colors. All things considered, 1998 was a good year for the
style-conscious. And from the look of things, 1999 is going to be
even better.
</P>
<P>
   A. Scott Walton writes for the Atlanta Journal-Constitution.
