CLINTON-EVIDECE (Undated) - While House Majority whip Tom DeLay
urges Senators to visit the highly secretive Judiciary Committee
evidence room, colleague J.D. Hayworth is stirring the same pot by
acting as a source on the mystery evidence for national news media
and calling KFYI at home. In the call to the local radio station,
Hayworth declined to reveal what he had seen in the room, but he
did permit himself to observe that is proved President Clinton is a
``sexual predator.'' Hayworth's actions are disturbing to at least
one member of Congress, who told The Republic that members were
told to keep the mystery evidence private and further that he had
already resolved not to look at it because it had not been
