<HEADLINE>
SANTA'S SECRET HELPER
</HEADLINE>
 (For use by NYTimes News Service clients) 
By KAREN CROUSE  
 c.1998 Los Angeles Daily News  
<TEXT>
<P>
   LOS ANGELES _ We made our list and checked it twice, from Tara
